NK039(ti)021:1: // dpal ldan lha mo'i bsad las dgra bgegs bsgral chog bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)021:4: sangs rgyas dkon mchog gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:5: dam chos dkon mchog gzu dang spang //
NK039(ti)021:6: dge 'dun dkon mchog gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:7: bla ma yi dam gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:8: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:9: chos skyongs srung ma gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:10: bka' yi lha srin sde brgyad gzu dang dpang //
NK039(ti)021:11: gzu dang dpang du dkon mchog bzhugs //
NK039(ti)021:13: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams na bzhugs pa yi //
NK039(ti)021:14: bla ma rig 'dzin rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK039(ti)021:15: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs ma lus kun //
NK039(ti)021:16: thugs rjes bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)021:18: bdag bsgrub pa po la dgra byung na //
NK039(ti)021:19: nga ma nyes ma len bsrung ma mkhyen //
NK039(ti)021:20: gzu dang dpang du dkon mchog bzhugs //
NK039(ti)021:21: zhal lce snang srid lha 'dres chod //
NK039(ti)021:22: dgra bgegs sdig can las ngan 'dis //
NK039(ti)021:23: dang po sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig /
NK039(ti)021:24: bar du dkon mchog dbu 'phang smad //
NK039(ti)021:25: tha ma gsang sngags gnyen po dral //
NK039(ti)021:26: da lta rnal 'byor bdag la bsngosa //
NK039(ti)021:27: las dge ba bcu ni khyad du bsad //
NK039(ti)021:28: mi dge bcu ni dang du blangs //
NK039(ti)021:30: 'di na bsgral ba'i zhing yin pa'i //
NK039(ti)021:31: da lta nyid du bsgral bar bya //
NK039(ti)021:32: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)021:33: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK039(ti)021:34: rngams brjid khro ba'i skur bzhengs la //
NK039(ti)021:35: dgra bgegs sdig can las ngan rnams //
NK039(ti)021:36: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)021:37: dzahmh'u bam hohbadz+ra ku sha ya dzah badz+ra pa sha h'u /
NK039(ti)021:40: badz+ra a kar+sha ya dza dzah na mo gu ru /
NK039(ti)021:41: bla tshol dus su lha mo re ma ti /
NK039(ti)021:42: mdun du bdud mo 'bum gyi ngo bo lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu zhes bya la /
NK039(ti)021:43: sku la lcags kyi tsha tsha 'phro /
NK039(ti)021:44: spyang ku'i mgo dgu yod pa /
NK039(ti)021:45: phyag g.yas na lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu /
NK039(ti)021:46: g.yon na zangs kyi 'phar ba lce brgyad 'gyed thabs su bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)021:47: sku la lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK039(ti)021:48: bskul ba byas pa tsam gyis mdun gyi ma mo
NK039(ti)021:49: dang sprul pa'i tshogs rnams myur du song nas dgra
NK039(ti)021:51: mdun gyi ling ga la thim par bsam /
NK039(ti)021:53: do nub nam gyi gung la babs //
NK039(ti)021:54: da lta tshogs kyi dus la bab //
NK039(ti)021:55: ma mo'i bla tshol dus la bab //
NK039(ti)021:56: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma //
NK039(ti)021:58: sku la cags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK039(ti)021:59: phyag ma g.yas na 'gyed pa ni //
NK039(ti)021:60: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu 'gyed //
NK039(ti)021:61: phyag ma g.yon na 'gyed pa ni //
NK039(ti)021:63: dung gi bya rgod glad na lding //
NK039(ti)021:64: bdud srin kun gyi mgon du che //
NK039(ti)021:65: srid pa gsum gyi bya ra mkhan //
NK039(ti)021:66: srid pa gsum du nyul zhing rgyug /
NK039(ti)021:67: legs nyes gnyis kyi shan 'byed ma //
NK039(ti)021:68: zas su dam nyams dgra bo'i sha la zo //
NK039(ti)021:69: skom du dam nyams dgra bo'i khrag la 'thung //
NK039(ti)021:70: dam nyams dgra bo'i bla 'khyams ma btang khug la shog /
NK039(ti)021:71: gzugs ling ga 'di la myur du khug /
NK039(ti)021:72: ming byang bu 'di la gnas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)021:73: ma h+aa ka la re m+aa ti /
NK039(ti)021:74: dgra bo n+ri ma ra ya khug dza /
NK039(ti)021:75: b+h+yoh dam nyams dgra bo'i bla tshe 'di //
NK039(ti)021:76: nam mkha'i khams su shor srid kyi //
NK039(ti)021:77: nam mkha'i khams su shor ba na //
NK039(ti)021:78: sring gcig rdo rje dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)021:79: bya rgyal khyung du skur sprul la //
NK039(ti)021:80: thang dkar rgod po pho nyar 'gyed //
NK039(ti)021:81: nam mkha'i khams nas ma btang khug la shog /
NK039(ti)021:82: dam nyams dgra bo'i bla tshe 'di //
NK039(ti)021:83: bar snang khams su shor srid kyi //
NK039(ti)021:84: bar snang khams su shor ba na //
NK039(ti)021:85: sring gcig rdo rje dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)021:86: rgod glag dag tu sku sprul pa //
NK039(ti)021:87: bswe yi glag mo pho nyar 'gyed //
NK039(ti)021:88: bar snang khams su ma btang khrid la shog /
NK039(ti)021:89: dam nyams dgra bo'i phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad dag tu shor srid kyi //
NK039(ti)021:90: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad dag tu sring gcig rdo rje
NK039(ti)021:91: lcags kyi spyang brgyad du lcags kyi khyi sder rkang
NK039(ti)021:92: gsum pho phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad ma btang dam nyams
NK039(ti)021:93: sa yi 'og tu shor srid kyi //
NK039(ti)021:94: sa yi 'og tu sring gcig rdo rje lcags kyi byi bar sku sprul la //
NK039(ti)021:95: zangs kyi byi ba mgo lnga pho sa yi 'og
NK039(ti)021:96: tu ma btang dam nyams dgra bo'i rgya mtsho'i gting
NK039(ti)021:98: rgya mtsho'i gting du shor sring gcig rdo rje chu
NK039(ti)021:99: srin rgyal mor sku nya chen yor po pho rgya
NK039(ti)021:100: mtsho'i gting du ma btang dam nyams gangs dkar rtse
NK039(ti)021:102: gangs dkar rtse la sring gcig dung gi seng ge sku sprul la //
NK039(ti)021:103: gangs byi dkar mor pho nyar 'gyed //
NK039(ti)021:104: gangs dkar rtse la ma btang khrid la shog /
NK039(ti)021:105: dam nyams dgra bo'i nyin ri dkar la shor srid kyang //
NK039(ti)021:106: nyin ri dkar la shor ba na //
NK039(ti)021:107: sring gcig rdo rje lcags kyi spyang kur sku nyin
NK039(ti)021:108: ri dkar la ma btang dam nyams srib ri nag
NK039(ti)021:110: srib ri nag la sring gcig gser gyi stag mo
NK039(ti)021:111: mgo lnga sku zangs kyi 'phar ba pho srib ri
NK039(ti)021:112: nag la ma btang dam nyams ban d+he'i lag tu
NK039(ti)021:113: shor srid kyang // ban d+he'i lag tu shor sring
NK039(ti)021:114: gcig phyag na rdo rje'i sku yangs dkar rgyal po
NK039(ti)021:115: pho ban d+he'i lag nas ma btang dam nyams bon
NK039(ti)021:116: po'i lag tu shor srid bon po'i lag tu sring
NK039(ti)021:117: gcig mgon po nag po'i sku klu bdud nag po'i
NK039(ti)021:118: pho bon po'i lag nas ma btang dam nyams dgra
NK039(ti)021:119: bo'i srog lha gnyen po'i lag tu shor srid kyang
NK039(ti)021:120: shor srid kyang // // srog lha gnyen po'i lag
NK039(ti)021:121: tu shor sring gcig rdo rje klu bdud gdug pa'i
NK039(ti)021:122: sku 'brug mo ngar chen pho srog lha gnyen po'i
NK039(ti)021:123: lag nas ma btang dam nyams dgra bo'i 'go ba'i
NK039(ti)021:124: lha lnga'i lag tu shor 'go ba'i lnga'i lag sring
NK039(ti)021:125: gcig zhing lpags dag tu sku sprul zhing dbyug dkar
NK039(ti)021:126: po'i pho 'go ba'i lha lnga'i lag nas ma btang
NK039(ti)021:127: dam nyams lus kyi lha lnga'i lag tu shor lus
NK039(ti)021:128: kyi lha lnga'i lag na sring gcig dung gi mon
NK039(ti)021:129: pa nag po dag tu sku zangs lcags bya khra
NK039(ti)021:130: nag po pho lus kyi lha lnga'i lag nas ma
NK039(ti)021:131: btang dam nyams phur bzlog mkhan gyi lag tu ma
NK039(ti)021:133: sngags bzlog mkhan gyi lag tu ma btang bsrung bzlog
NK039(ti)021:134: mkhan gyi lag tu ma rdzas bzlog mkhan gyi lag
NK039(ti)021:135: tu ma mtho ri rab rtse nas ma btang khrid
NK039(ti)021:136: la shog / dma' rgya mtsho'i gting nas ma bar
NK039(ti)021:137: 'dzam bu'i gling nas ma sra ba brag la bab
NK039(ti)021:138: kyang snyi ba chu la bab kyang ma 'phyo ba
NK039(ti)021:139: chu la bab kyang ma dam nyams dgra bo'i bla
NK039(ti)021:140: 'khyams ma btang gzugs ling ga 'di la myur du
NK039(ti)021:141: la shog / khrid la shog / ming byang bu 'di la gnas par gyur //
NK039(ti)021:142: dam nyams dgra bo'i las ngan 'di //
NK039(ti)021:143: des byed ma mos des la shog /
NK039(ti)021:144: 'dren byed ma mos drangs la shog /
NK039(ti)021:145: 'gug byed ma mos khug la shog /
NK039(ti)021:146: 'ded byed ma mos ded la shog /
NK039(ti)021:148: bstod byed ma mos bstod la shog /
NK039(ti)021:149: gsod byed ma mos gsod la shog /
NK039(ti)021:150: rang dbang med par 'dir khug la //
NK039(ti)021:151: gzugs ling ga 'di la khug la shog /
NK039(ti)021:152: mtshan byang bu 'di la gnas par gyur //
NK039(ti)021:153: thogs pa med par da sgrol cig /
NK039(ti)021:154: tshe bsod bkrags mdangs drod dbugs rnams //
NK039(ti)021:155: bdud mo re ma ti'i da phrog la //
NK039(ti)021:156: glo snying nang rol bcas pa rnams //
NK039(ti)021:157: dpal ldan ma yi rngam zas gyis //
NK039(ti)021:158: sha khrag rus gsum thams cad kyang //
NK039(ti)021:159: ma mo'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs su bzhes //
NK039(ti)021:160: ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti //
NK039(ti)021:161: dgra bo n+ri ma ra ya dza dzah zhes bla tshul 'gugs legs so //
NK039(ti)021:163: bstan la sdang ba'i dgra bo 'di //
NK039(ti)021:164: bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa yin //
NK039(ti)021:165: 'go ba'i lha lnga la sogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)021:166: bsrang byed lha rnams kun gyis kyang //
NK039(ti)021:167: sdig can 'di la bsrung bar ma byed par //
NK039(ti)021:168: dam nyams dgra 'di myur du spangs //
NK039(ti)021:169: sdig can dgra yi gshed mdzod cig /

NK039(ti)021:171: dgra bo n+ri ma ra ya shag phye //
NK039(ti)021:173: dgra bo'i pho lha 'phrag pa g.yas nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:174: ma lha 'phrag pa g.yon nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:175: zhang lha spyi bo'i gtsug nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:176: nye lha rkang pa'i mthil nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:177: srog lha snying gi dkyil nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:178: sgra lha rtag pa'i rgyab nas phyes //
NK039(ti)021:179: lhan cig skyes pa'i lha dang phyes //
NK039(ti)021:180: mnyam por 'ong ba'i bdud dang sprod //
NK039(ti)021:182: sa la brten pa'i rten phur phud //
NK039(ti)021:183: gri thabs nyi shu rtsa lngas sod //
NK039(ti)021:184: bdun rgyud tshun chad ma btang bar //

NK039(ti)021:186: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti //
NK039(ti)021:187: dgra bo n+ri ma ra ya shag phyes //
NK039(ti)021:189: rlung spros lha mo nag mo ste /
NK039(ti)021:190: g.yas kyi gri gug srog rtsa rgal nas gcod //
NK039(ti)021:191: g.yon gyi thod khrag sems kyi mar me sod //
NK039(ti)021:192: bdud rtsi h'u gi ngo bo phrog par bya //
NK039(ti)021:193: 'bud pa'i rlung gi mar me gsod par bya //
NK039(ti)021:194: drangs ba'i rlung gi thig le drangs par bya //
NK039(ti)021:195: drug cu rtsa gnyis thun gyi dmigs bya sod //
NK039(ti)021:197: bdag gi sna bug g.yas nas rlung sngo dmar spros pa'i rtse mo las /
NK039(ti)021:198: b+h+yo nag mo gcig 'phros pa'i bsgrub bya'i sna bug g.yon du zhugs pa'am /

NK039(ti)021:203: bu de la brgyab pas nag gam gyis btang bar
NK039(ti)021:204: bsam / de nas gzung thag lag tu bzung la /
NK039(ti)021:205: kho'i srog rtsa nas bzung bar bsam la sngags bzlas

NK039(ti)021:208: phur bu lha mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis smad phur
NK039(ti)021:209: ba mgar gyi sol me nas byung ba ltar dmar
NK039(ti)021:214: snying ka lte ba rnams su btabs pa'i thal gyis phur bar bsam zhing /
NK039(ti)021:215: b+h+yoh phur zor bsrung ma re ma ti //
NK039(ti)021:216: dam la ma 'da' da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)021:217: lcags sam drag po'i shing rnams la //
NK039(ti)021:218: mngon spyod drag po'i phur bu byas //
NK039(ti)021:219: spyi bor rgya mdud gzhal yas khang //
NK039(ti)021:220: rked pa rgya mdud dpal ldan ma //
NK039(ti)021:221: rtse mo zur gsum re ma ti //
NK039(ti)021:222: spyi bor rgya mdud 'brug stong ldir //
NK039(ti)021:223: rked pa rgya mdud glog stong 'gyu //
NK039(ti)021:224: rtse mo zur gsum me ltar 'bar //
NK039(ti)021:225: me ltar 'bar ba'i rtse mo na //

NK039(ti)021:271: khyod kyi las kyi pho nya ni //

NK039(ti)021:423: gsang sngags kun gyi mchod len ma //
NK039(ti)021:424: rnal 'byor kun gyi sku bsrungs ma //
NK039(ti)021:425: bdag gis gdung ste bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)021:426: de tshe khyod kyi thun rgyob la //
NK039(ti)021:427: thun khrag rims su bsgyur du gsol //
NK039(ti)021:428: rims nad dgra la dbab tu gsol //
NK039(ti)021:429: sdang sems gnod sems ldan pa yi //
NK039(ti)021:430: ming rus gzugs su bris pa la //

NK039(ti)021:466: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //

NK039(ti)021:468: dgra bo n+ri ma ra ya thun b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)021:469: de nas mtshon cha rnams lag tu bzungs la /
NK039(ti)021:470: rang nyid yi dam lha'i nga rgyal gyis 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)021:472: nga ni dus gsum bzhugs pa yi //
NK039(ti)021:473: sangs rgyas yin te ye shes sku //
NK039(ti)021:474: ye shes rno dbal mtshon cha yi //

NK039(ti)021:488: rgya gram rno dbal dgra bgegs log rtog h+aum /

NK039(ti)021:492: pad ma rab tu 'bar ba dang //
NK039(ti)021:493: rgya gram rab tu 'bar ba dang //

NK039(ti)021:598: // 'jig rten dreg pa'i tshogs bcas kyi //
